ShotFX version 3.0 is officially launched! Update to get a fresh experience and make more splendid FX videos with new effect. Brand new front page UI! Neat and clear making it easier to find the effect you want in various categories now. Merge effect: shoot effect video with background and foreground at same time. New experience of 3D wraparound magical world.
